    "title": "SeaKing Leaning Post Top Only - BLK (700mm x 280mm)",
    "body_html": "<p>Free Shipping in Australia</p>\n<div data-content-field=\"excerpt\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<p class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Designed for the serious offshore fisherman, this leaning post is heavy duty with an aluminium plate fibreglassed in for post mounting that will give you piece of mind while fighting your dream pelagic fish offshore in those hairy conditions. Hand made with full composite materials of the highest quality.</p>\n<p class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Inclusions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Leaning Post Top</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Dimensions: 700mm x 280mm</p>\n<p class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Prices include GST.</p>\n</div>\n<div data-animation-role=\"content\" data-item-id=\"63c8c932f51fc8571dfd66b3\" class=\"product-quantity-input\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><br></div>",
